    "data": [
        {
            "title": "警錦田公路設路障截毒品快餐車拘2男女 檢2.9萬元可卡因及K仔",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/addd2b48e57cb4d31f5281e39c68fecc/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250329/_2025032906084832007.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>警方表示，新界北總區交通部特遣隊人員，周五（28日）晚上於錦田公路近高埔村設置路障期間，發現一輛私家車形跡可疑，遂截停調查。人員其後在女乘客身上檢獲52包合共重約重24克的懷疑可卡因及少量懷疑氯胺酮。案件中檢獲的毒品總市值約2.9萬元。\n\n</p>\n<p>經初步調查，姓沈（23歲）男司機及姓詹（21歲）女乘客涉嫌「販運危險藥物」被捕，現正被扣留調查。案件交由元朗警區刑事調查隊第八隊跟進。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2060873/即時-港聞-警錦田公路設路障截毒品快餐車拘2男女-檢2-9萬元可卡因及K仔",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-29 06:21:21",
