        {
            "title": "灣仔29歲女軒尼詩道遭非禮 59歲印度男被捕",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"案件交由灣仔警區刑事調查隊第九隊跟進。資料圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/2994ca42e6a532766a270aeae5e54682/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250329/_2025032904135241481.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">案件交由灣仔警區刑事調查隊第九隊跟進。資料圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>灣仔發生非禮案。周五（28日）晚上11時許，據報，一名29歲女子在灣仔軒尼詩道一巴士站遭一名男子非禮。人員接報到場，該名59歲印度籍男子涉嫌非禮被捕，現正被扣留調查。案件交由灣仔警區刑事調查隊第九隊跟進。據了解，被捕男子持行街紙。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2060869/即時-港聞-灣仔29歲女軒尼詩道遭非禮-59歲印度男被捕",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-29 04:21:21",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "警荃灣搗破非去釣魚機賭檔拘捕9人 檢2釣魚機及2千元賭款",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"警荃灣搗破非去釣魚機賭檔拘捕9人。警方圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/3230d47b3fd12d9af79fbe948eeec78d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250329/_2025032903121041015.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">警荃灣搗破非去釣魚機賭檔拘捕9人。警方圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>荃灣警區反三合會行動組人員經深入調查後，昨日（28日）晚上約8時突擊搜查德士古道一單位，搗破一個懷疑非法釣魚機賭檔。\n\n</p>\n<p>該單位內一名44歲姓陳本地男負責人涉嫌「經營賭博場所」被捕；另外2名內地男子、5名本地男子及一名本地女子，年齡介乎21至61歲，則涉嫌「在賭博場所內賭博」被捕。當中，一名35歲姓吳本地男子同時涉嫌「沒有攜帶身分證明文件」被捕。\n\n</p>\n<p>行動中，人員共檢獲兩部釣魚機、兩部遊戲機、一批遊戲卡及二千元現金。所有被捕人現正被扣留調查。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164670/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方共檢獲兩部釣魚機、兩部遊戲機、一批遊戲卡及二千元現金。警方圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a1e148420d8ec669a30e6cb89f837fa7/2025-03/Gambling_2.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方共檢獲兩部釣魚機、兩部遊戲機、一批遊戲卡及二千元現金。警方圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>根據香港法例一百四十八章《賭博條例》，「經營賭博場所」及「在賭博場所內賭博」屬嚴重罪行，前者一經定罪最高可判罰款五百萬元及監禁七年，後者一經定罪最高可判罰款三萬元及監禁九個月。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2060868/即時-港聞-警荃灣搗破非去釣魚機賭檔拘捕9人-檢2釣魚機及2千元賭款",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-29 03:26:28",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        }
    ]
